{"tid":673622,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"辛迪卡索拉宣佈決定離開阿仙奴","createTime":"2018-05-22T04:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T06:18:54.000Z","uid":31314,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"700a2c95c0dd5d7eab0a99d62587ccc40b8fa053","tid":673622,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:06:12.000Z","msg":"除了公佈來季球衣號碼出現變動外，阿仙奴同日另一個消息是養傷多時的辛迪卡索拉決定離隊。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴於周一官方宣佈，<span style=\"color: red;\">效力球會6年的辛迪卡索拉（Santi Cazorla）在季尾約滿後不會續約</span>，而卡索拉亦隨即透過社交網絡，向球迷作出真情告別：「阿仙奴球迷們，我為經過那麼多美好時光後離開感到傷心，我愛在球會的日子，將會一時常掛念我們一起有過的特別時刻。你給予我特別的支持，我會懷念你們。謝謝每一位。」 卡索拉近年一直受足腱傷困擾，自2016年10月以來不曾再為阿仙奴上陣。 這位前西班牙國腳於2012年從馬拉加來投，6年來合共上陣180場射入29球，協助球隊羸過兩次足總盃及兩次社區盾，而其中代表作是2014年足總盃決賽施展百步穿楊，協助球隊以3:2反勝侯城捧盃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/PuABt8IUbkerK/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FPuABt8IUbkerK%2Fgiphy.gif&h=a4867c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/4fe7e009dd5906a0ae2ee9215a0c98c4/tumblr_ojejs37Z4s1qcaj1no3_250.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F4fe7e009dd5906a0ae2ee9215a0c98c4%2Ftumblr_ojejs37Z4s1qcaj1no3_250.gif&h=a6b77655&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7274412913f766e7262668c44405511a0e9a8ac8","tid":673622,"uid":9347,"like":7,"dislike":29,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"又多一隻25狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40a6076595d0f1db40518b61807ad9f9ae125ff","tid":673622,"uid":160414,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:10:18.000Z","msg":"全盛時期佢都幾撚勁嘅"},{"pid":"ccd26aca7e01de81f47c099aa70f244966e5f4ea","tid":673622,"uid":59818,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"c40a6076595d0f1db40518b61807ad9f9ae125ff","tid":673622,"uid":160414,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:10:18.000Z","msg":"全盛時期佢都幾撚勁嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":